         <abstract id="aspace_9dcc09fa44ab6c5f4d389dc85f2e6afd">The records consist of files maintained by Rollin G. Osterweis documenting the Yale Divisional Major program. Included are printed materials, memoranda, statements and gradesheets of divisional major students, and hand-outs from the Yale Human Culture and Behavior program.</abstract>
